title: Vero_Visi_Series_v15.0_Multilanguage
description:
VISI 
   is acknowledged as one of the  world&#039;s leading PC based design and
   manufacturing solutions  for the mould & die industries.  It  offers  a
   unique combination of applications, fully integrated wireframe, surface
   and   solid   modelling,   comprehensive 2D,  3D  and 5 axis  machining
   strategies  with  dedicated   high speed  routines.   Industry specific
   applications for plastic injection tool design including  material flow
   analysis and progressive die design with step-by-step unfolding provide
   the toolmaker with unsurpassed levels of productivity.
